_sText:
Hello guys ! (sorry for my bad english)

In this map, you have to avoid the propellers to have a weapon.
For exemple, If you arrive on the 2nd level, you have a gun.
             If you arrive on the 3rd level, you have a mp5navy.

There are 4 level (knife, gun, mp5navy, awp).
When everyone has finished, everyone are teleport in an area to kill their enemies.

It's a very funny map with a design and a gameplay pleasant.
This map requires NoBlock.

Good game and enjoy !

HAVE FUN !

VISIT http://www.niko-mapping-studio.tk/
